=== Birth ===
{{multiple image
| align     = right
| direction = horizontal
| header   = 
| width     = 
<!-- Image 1 -->
| image1    = Atuell en forma d'Afrodita en una petxina, Àtica, necròpolis de Fanagoria, pinínsula de Taman. Primer quart del segle IV aC, ceràmica.JPG
| width1    = 210
| alt1      =
| caption1  = Early fourth-century BC [[Attica|Attic]] pottery vessel in the shape of Aphrodite inside a shell from the [[Phanagoria]] cemetery in the [[Taman Peninsula]]
<!-- Image 2 -->
| image2    = Aphrodites Rock.jpg
| width2    = 330
| alt2      =
| caption2  = [[Petra tou Romiou]] ("The rock of the [[Greeks|Greek]]"), Aphrodite's legendary birthplace in [[Paphos]], Cyprus
